Install CLI (anywhere on PATH):
  mise run setup
  # or: uv tool install --force --editable .

Refresh / uninstall:
  mise run install-cli
  mise run uninstall-cli

Dev:
  mise run install
  mise run test          # coverage ≥90%
  mise run test-fast

Help (keep in sync with README behavior table):
  redact help
  redact help patterns
  redact help exclude
  unredact -h

Dry-run / config:
  redact -n src/
  redact patterns init|list|add|remove
  redact exclude init|list|add|remove   # .git/** in starter excludes

Always skipped: .git/ (and other tool dirs), binary/image extensions, non-UTF-8.
Branch: master (not main).

Remaining work: see TODO.md
